      <div class="msgContentFrame">Not using your shield would make you take more damage, but also allow you to parry more, which will give you good sword SP. So you could try that if your healers can keep you alive. <br /> <br />My only other recommendation would be ... don't fight high physical defense mobs like Crabs. You will always get poor SP gains fighting them, because you are hitting them for such small damage. <br /> <br />You could try the Fat Dodos near Cedarwood instead (not sure where you guys are fighting and what lvl you are), but you should see more gains from them, as you will be hitting them 10 times harder.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=1385155" rel="external nofollow" title="lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=1385155">[img]<a href="http://sigs.enjin.com/sig-ffxiv/7865_7d8fe305bfae897b.png" title="http://sigs.enjin.com/sig-ffxiv/7865_7d8fe305bfae897b.png" rel="external nofollow">http://sigs.enjin.com/sig-ffxiv/7865_7d8fe305bfae897b.png</a>[/img]</a></div></div>
