      <div class="msgContentFrame">Well 2 week ago, I (GLD20) was killing some wolf with a friend (CON23). He was getting like 200-300 most of the time and i was getting like 100-200 for my Sword and 150-250 for my Shield. At the time i was only doing thing like Voke (a lot), hit, guard, and some WS. After some reading about GLD, i decide to change some way of tanking. Yesterday we went for kill the same Wolf at the same rank, i was using Voke only at the start, Guard, Phalanx a lot and hit some, and my SP was like 200-300 most of the time when his was still 200-300 like last time and was keeping the hate better to, even without using voke all the time. Seems like Phalanx help a lot for SP (I have gain 100+ SP from a Phalanx).<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/965232.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
